# iOS Configuration

This directory contains iOS-specific configuration files.

## Structure

```
ios/
├── {{PROJECT_NAME}}/
│   ├── AppDelegate.h
│   ├── AppDelegate.mm
│   ├── Info.plist
│   └── LaunchScreen.storyboard
├── {{PROJECT_NAME}}.xcodeproj/
├── {{PROJECT_NAME}}.xcworkspace/
├── Podfile
└── Pods/
```

## Setup

Install CocoaPods dependencies:

```bash
cd ios
pod install
```

## Running on iOS

```bash
# From project root
npm run ios

# Specific simulator
npm run ios -- --simulator="iPhone 15 Pro"
```

## Build for Release

1. Open Xcode:
```bash
open ios/{{PROJECT_NAME}}.xcworkspace
```

2. Select "Product" > "Archive"
3. Follow Apple's distribution guide

## Signing

Configure signing in Xcode:
1. Open workspace in Xcode
2. Select project in navigator
3. Select target
4. Go to "Signing & Capabilities"
5. Select your team and provisioning profile

## Common Issues

### Pod install fails
```bash
cd ios
pod deintegrate
pod install
```

### Clean build
```bash
cd ios
rm -rf build
rm -rf ~/Library/Developer/Xcode/DerivedData
```

### Simulator issues
```bash
xcrun simctl erase all
```

